cs.SD, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.LG 

The paper deals with sound event recognition in web videos, which involves information retrieval (IR) and multimedia (MM) processing. It also involves machine learning (ML) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques, which fall under the categories of statistical learning (cs.LG) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.SD (Sound), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.MM (Multimedia). The other two sub-categories, cs.CL and cs.LG, are less likely but still relevant to the paper's content.
